{"tid":2009603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近排警隊內發生嘅野十足十共產黨派一貫做嘢方式","createTime":"2020-05-10T00:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T10:38:19.000Z","uid":41423,"like":86,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a5075495b4bea8f2c6d7cb986773850e39f298ab","tid":2009603,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:44:25.000Z","msg":"唔理佢哋有冇內部鬥爭緊，或只係想spin視線保住大粒,<br />\n<br />\n但講到打壓平民時，唔同派系既目標仍是一致的<br />\n因為打壓示威者先係佢地嘅統一戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「 聯合次要敵人，打擊主要敵人」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家依然各有崗位<br />\n<br />\n想煮死班差佬嘅繼續做，<br />\n<br />\n想貼文宣嘅繼續做，<br />\n<br />\n想立法會35+發揮對政府議案嘅影響力，將體制內嘅民意授權變成國際線嘅彈藥嘅繼續做，<br />\n<br />\n不論你相信勇武又好；國際線攬炒港共又好；立會35+又好，敵人永遠都係中共港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d176dd6b1178e4acf4f677a4779edd0e4c0600d7","tid":2009603,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:45:52.000Z","msg":"完全同意"},{"pid":"5c43dd9bff83ec8fb65e921f9282b513cae46928","tid":2009603,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b33003f26e37f082df03f57c6b46818ef78c17f","tid":2009603,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:47:04.000Z","msg":"懶人包發明咗之後<br />\n應該要有人整合狂推"},{"pid":"718423aee108529dc0a6566ab1129c25e618bf1b","tid":2009603,"uid":56698,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n因為打壓示威者先係佢地嘅統一戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「 聯合次要敵人，打擊主要敵人」<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n正確而言，統一戰線喺打壓香港人<br />\n日常生活都已經蝦蝦霸霸"},{"pid":"e56cbee1d3229595a8ebb1e4d2d80bf4cf31c801","tid":2009603,"uid":41608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":